  <span id="freeText12782684895031980245" style="display:none">Not usually possible for me to read a 900-page in one day but when the day includes 5 hours in an A&amp;E waiting room things do conspire. Somehow I'd not read this novel before and I'd forgotten how long Binchy's early ones are, but honestly you couldn't ask for better, more gentle or more compelling company.</span>
